      <enclosure url='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sayo-melu/sayo-cast/master/asset/1-1%20host%20podcast%20on%20jekyll%20(在%20jekyll%20上托管播客).m4a' length='280'/>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;feel free to host audio podcast with &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/sayo-melu/jekyll-podcast&quot;&gt;jekyll-podcast&lt;/a&gt; on jekyll.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;why-do-i-build-jekyll-podcast&quot;&gt;why do i build jekyll-podcast&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;uploading podcasts is not as easy as uploading videos, you have to own or borrow a web server to host your content.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;there are a lot of platforms for people to upload podcasts, but some of them spend your money, some of them cannot be configured to your requirement.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;although there are also some podcast holding solutions for jekyll, they are difficult to use. and they don’t have a solution to generate web pages for your podcast.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;to solve these problems, i build this configurable jekyll-podcast. you can host it on &lt;a href=&quot;http://github.com&quot;&gt;github&lt;/a&gt; for free, so you can buy you a better 🎙 microphone.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;how-to-use&quot;&gt;how to use&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;check &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/sayo-melu/jekyll-podcast&quot;&gt;jekyll-podcast&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;sample&quot;&gt;sample&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;my &lt;a href=&quot;https://sayo-melu.github.io/podcast.xml&quot;&gt;podcast&lt;/a&gt; on my &lt;a href=&quot;http://sayo-melu.github.io&quot;&gt;blog&lt;/a&gt; hosted on github.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;reference&quot;&gt;reference&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://help.apple.com/itc/podcasts_connect/#/itcb54353390&quot;&gt;A podcaster’s guide to RSS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://help.apple.com/itc/podcasts_connect/#/itcbaf351599&quot;&gt;RSS feed sample&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://developers.google.com/search/docs/data-types/podcast&quot;&gt;Podcast&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://help.apple.com/itc/podcasts_connect/#/itc9267a2f12&quot;&gt;Apple Podcasts categories&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;host&quot;&gt;host&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;  &lt;li&gt;sayo melu: &lt;a href=&quot;https://sayo-melu.xyz&quot;&gt;sayo-melu.xyz&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;contact&quot;&gt;contact&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;  &lt;li&gt;blog + podcast: &lt;a href=&quot;https://sayo-melu.xyz&quot;&gt;https://sayo-melu.xyz&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;webpage + comment: &lt;a href=&quot;/host-podcast-on-jekyll/&quot;&gt;https://sayo-melu.xyz/host-podcast-on-jekyll/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;  &lt;li&gt;email: &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:sayo-cast@outlook.com&quot;&gt;sayo-cast@outlook.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
